These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola
There 2 different types of food: radish, cranberry
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola  | iced-tea |
| Food       | radish | cranberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta |
| Sport      | cricket     | baseball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian
1. the brazilian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | zombie  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | egyptian |

 #################################

 
