.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, italian
2 different pets are kept: ferret, pony
1. the italian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | japanese | italian |
| Pet           | pony     | ferret  |

