The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, roller
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |
| Sport       | surfing  | skateboarding |
| Transport   | bus | roller |

